title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Yuanbao Collectibles
content:
Invite prosperity into your life for the year ahead by searching for new Yuanbao Collectibles hidden around Los Santos. Each one found awards GTA$ and RP, with a special bonus for collecting all 36.

If you’re looking for some roadside assistance to locate these across Southern San Andreas, upgrade your Benefactor Terrorbyte at the Garment Factory with the new Collectible Scanner from Agents of Sabotage.
